Roba Little Stars aankleedkussen

Roba Little Stars changing mat

This changing mat has a soft lining, making it super comfortable for your baby. The raised edges on three sides provide extra safety when changing. And thanks to the coating, you can easily clean the changing mat with a cloth. 100% phthalate free.

Specifications:
Colour: grey
Print colour: white
Gender: junior
Material: plastic (100% Phthalate free)
